Title: C-Like 'getopt' Behavior
Version: 1.20.4
Authors@R: c(person("Trevor L", "Davis", role=c("aut", "cre"), email="trevor.l.davis@gmail.com"),
    person("Allen", "Day", role="aut", comment="Original package author"),
